videos.description: Iowa State's Nazareth Mitrou-Long drains the 3-pointer to tie the game, but Gonzaga answers with a 3-pointer from Nigel Williams-Goss as both teams are hot from the field early on.
videos.headline: Iowa State, Gonzaga shooting the lights out early

videos.description: GONZ Jordan Mathews made Layup then  Monte Morris hits 3-pointer on other end for Iowa State
videos.headline: Bulldogs, Cyclones continue to put on impressive shooting display

videos.description: GONZ Josh Perkins made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Jordan Mathews.
videos.headline: Perkins gives Gonzaga double-digit lead

videos.description: Gonzaga is firing on all cylinders so far against Iowa State, punctuated when Przemek Karnowski throws the pass behind his head right to Jonathan Williams for the two-hand dunk.
videos.headline: Behind-the-head pass leads to massive dunk for Gonzaga

videos.description: Iowa State head coach Steve Prohm wants his offense to slow down
videos.headline: Iowa State head coach Steve Prohm wants his offense to slow down

videos.description: Monte Morris' makes the sweet pass to Matt Thomas on the back door cut for the layup that is sparking Iowa State's comeback against Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Sweet back door cut sparking Iowa State comeback

videos.headline: Burton catching fire for Iowa State
